ğŸ›‘ While Loop

âœ… They are used to execute a block of code a repeatedly until the set condition gets satisfied

âœ… Types of while loops

    Doâ€¦ while â€“     executes the block of code at least once before evaluating the condition
    Whileâ€¦ â€“    checks the condition first. If it evaluates to true, the block of code is executed as long as the condition is true. 
                If it evaluates to false, the execution of the while loop is terminated.

